 </datafield>
 <datafield tag="999" ind1="C" ind2="5">
  <subfield code="m">so the 1&lt;j\leqslant n contraction patterns of {{\nabla}^{n-1}}\xi are λ-reducible. In addition, the λ-reducibility of the j = 2 pattern implies the λ-reducibility of the j = 1 pattern</subfield>
